mapper.select:
SELECT "DbV2002Fuka"."choteiNendo" AS 調定年度, "DbV2002Fuka"."fukaNendo" AS 賦課年度, "DbV2002Fuka"."tsuchishoNo" AS 通知書番号, "DbV2002Fuka"."hihokenshaNo" AS 被保険者番号, "DbV2002Fuka"."shikibetsuCode" AS 識別コード, "DbV2002Fuka"."fukaShichosonCode" AS 賦課市町村コード, "DbV2002Fuka"."tkSaishutsuKampuGaku" AS 特徴歳出還付額, "DbV2002Fuka"."fuSaishutsuKampuGaku" AS 普徴歳出還付額, "DbT2003Kibetsu"."ki" AS 期, "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choshuHouhou" AS 徴収方法, "UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu"."choteigaku" AS 調定額, A."CaV0702shunyugaku" AS 収入額
FROM rgdb."DbV2002Fuka" AS "DbV2002Fuka" INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT2003Kibetsu" AS "DbT2003Kibetsu" ON "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choteiNendo" = "DbV2002Fuka"."choteiNendo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."fukaNendo" = "DbV2002Fuka"."fukaNendo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."tsuchishoNo" = "DbV2002Fuka"."tsuchishoNo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."rirekiNo" = "DbV2002Fuka"."rirekiNo" INNER JOIN rgdb."UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu" AS "UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu" ON "UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu"."choteiId" = "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choteiId" LEFT JOIN rgca."CaFt702FindTotalShunyu"(0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 2, NULL, 0, 0) AS A ON "UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu"."shunoId" = A."UrT0700shunoId"
INNER JOIN rgdb."DbV2503TokuchoHikazeiNenkinHantei" AS "DbV2503" ON "DbT2003Kibetsu"."tsuchishoNo" = "DbV2503"."tsuchishoNo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choteiNendo" = "DbV2503"."choteiNendo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."fukaNendo" = "DbV2503"."kazeiNendo" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."ki" = "DbV2503"."ki" and "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choshuHouhou" = '1'
WHERE "DbV2002Fuka"."choteiNendo" IN (#{対象年},#{対象年minus1})
AND "DbV2002Fuka"."fukaShichosonCode" = #{市町村コード} ORDER BY "DbV2002Fuka"."choteiNendo" DESC, "DbV2002Fuka"."fukaNendo" DESC, "DbV2002Fuka"."tsuchishoNo" DESC, "DbT2003Kibetsu"."choshuHouhou" DESC, "DbT2003Kibetsu"."ki" DESC
